Security testing:
1.	Verify the web page which contains important data (e.g. password, credit card numbers, secret answers for security question, etc) should be submitted via HTTPS (SSL).
2.	Verify registration, login, change password function correctly (add forgot password?).
3.	Verify the important information (e.g. password, credit card numbers etc) should display in encrypted format (dot).
4.	Make sure orders can be submitted to the correct place
Functional testing:
5.	Check all the links are directed correctly
6.	Check all the buttons work correctly
7.	All mandatory fields should be validated and indicated by an asterisk (*) symbol.	
Usability testing:
8.	Check all items have correct images and prices
9.	Check spelling and grammatical errors
10.	Check all fonts are suitable (headings and contents)
